trans-unit.source:

Рекомендуемое максимальное количество синхронизируемых записей - 5000.
trans-unit.target:
Configure synchronization filters to limit the amount of records to be synchronized to Outlook.
Total synchronization time increases as more data is allowed to be synchronized. Filters can help to reduce the synchronization time required by reducing the number of records to synchronize.
For optimal synchronization performance, it is recommended to maintain filters that do not allow more than 5,000 records to be synchronized.

Information is automatically synchronized between $pim_name$k and $remote_app_name$ at a preset frequency.

The synchronization process will download accessible information based on business rules and current synchronization filters.
